data.description: VA ASSUMPTION OPPORTUNITY @ 2.25% with qualification. UPDATED, IMMACULATE and MOVE-IN READY pool home located on a corner lot with a dream backyard in a smaller close-knit community!   This beautiful Valrico home features four large bedrooms, two full baths, large laundry room and fully fenced yard perfect for family entertaining. As you pull up to the driveway you will notice the meticulously kept lawn, towering oak tree and freshly painted exterior along with a lovely paved porch and leaded glass enter door with a leaded glass panel for extra light. Entering the home, notice the three large front windows that make the home light and bright and add an element of design to the space. The bright, sunny feeling continues into the kitchen with windows looking out to the large pool area. The kitchen boasts new quartz countertops, new stainless steel appliances and breakfast bar.  The large family room is sure to be the favorite spot in the house with a stone-faced fireplace and large hearth, perfect for chilly winter nights and a dream to decorate for the holidays. The four large bedrooms and two full baths allow for ample room for the family to spread out and enjoy their own space. Step outside of the new sliding glass doors onto the fully paved screened-in pool and lanai and find yourself in your own peaceful paradise. The large fully fenced backyard with lush lawn and towering oak trees is the perfect place to gather the family for weekend BBQ’s, games and parties. It is the perfect outdoor escape. The roof on the home was replaced in 2018 and the air conditioner is six years new. The list of upgrades and updates on this home is impressive, with new interior and exterior paint, ALL new upgraded windows and sliding doors throughout, new lighting fixtures, new chimney stone, new ceiling fans and ALL new window blinds are just a few of the upgrades this beautiful home offers. Reserve your showing time today to see this amazing home that is sure to check all the boxes off your list and then some!  Located close to schools, shopping, restaurants, gyms, and medical offices.
